    "name": "Lugh",
    "epitet": "Anima Child",
    "display": "Lugh: Anima Child",
    "description": "A boy from an orphanage. Raigh's twin brother. He's cheerful and tender-hearted. Appears in Fire Emblem: The Binding Blade.",
    "artist": "Himukai Yuji (日向悠二)",
    "voiceActorEN": "Michael Johnston",
    "voiceActorJP": "竹内順子",
    "dialogue": [
        {
            "text": "Hello, I'm Lugh! I may look a little inexperienced, but I'm good with magic. It's great to be here!",
            "context": "joined"
        },
        {
            "text": "Chad is clever, but he doesn't like to study. Raigh is a genius, but he's impossible to get along with. Will those two be all right without me around?",
            "context": "castle"
        },
        {
            "text": "We originally lived in a small orphanage, but the war with Bern threw things into chaos. I really hope everybody is doing all right.",
            "context": "castle"
        },
        {
            "text": "I saw you talking to some pretty important-looking people just now! Thanks for everything you do. If there's anything I can do to help out, just let me know!",
            "context": "castle"
        },
        {
            "text": "I managed to get my hands on a cartload of baked goods... You want some? I'm happy to share!",
            "context": "castle"
        },
        {
            "text": "Do you have a moment? I'm not quite sure I understand this part of the book I'm reading... Can you help?",
            "context": "castle"
        },
        {
            "text": "Hello there, <Player Name>! My name's Lugh. I'm glad to meet you.",
            "context": "friend"
        },
        {
            "text": "I see... So this is the spirit of magic.",
            "context": "level"
        },
        {
            "text": "I'm doing the best that I can!",
            "context": "level"
        },
        {
            "text": "Maybe I'm not cut out for this after all...",
            "context": "level"
        },
        {
            "text": "Wow! What is this power? I can use it? Thank you!",
            "context": "growth"
        },
        {
            "text": "Hey, <Player Name>... How am I doing in battle? Am I pulling my weight? I don't really like all this fighting...so I got a bit concerned that I might be causing you some consternation. Where I come from, they killed the caretaker of our orphanage, and I found myself fighting for revenge. It was scary... But once I thought about Raigh, Chad, and the others... that gave me the courage I needed. I want to do everything I can for you, you see. I like you a lot. You can count on me!",
            "context": "maxed"
        }
    ],
